LICENSE PLACEHOLDER

This file is a placeholder applied by the Cinatra extension extraction script
ONLY when the source package does not already ship a LICENSE file.

The effective license for this extension is recorded in the package.json
"license" field. The extraction script maps it as follows:

  - wordpress-agent, drupal-agent  -> GPL-2.0-or-later
  - every other extracted extension -> the source package.json "license",
                                        defaulting to Apache-2.0

Before publishing, replace this placeholder with the full, verbatim text of the
license named in package.json (the SPDX-standard license body — e.g. the full
Apache License 2.0 text, or the GNU General Public License v2 text).
